      "id": "737830",
      "is_folded": false,
      "answerer": {
        "username": "freepapers",
        "uid": "118140"
      },
      "contents": "<div class=\"markitup-box\">\n\t\t\t其实，毛不是一个人，而是一群人。<br/>\n<br/>\n他真正是可悲可恨奴性狡狯的中国人的代表。\t\t</div>",
